oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Eura Trice
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The mother of Louis E. Trice, II, Eura Trice, in a rocking chair holding a dog. Louis was born in Dallas, Texas to Louis E. Trice and Eura Parmer Trice in 1914. His father was born and raised in Montgomery County, Tennessee.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Families; Dogs
